name: 泰勒·鲁维埃
birth_place: 美国,佛罗里达州,迈阿密
introduction: Taylor Rouviere was born in Miami, Florida. She has three siblings, Zachary, Koby and Sydney who can also be seen in well-known TV shows and films. Taylor enjoyed success as a youngster appearing in hundreds of print and commercial campaigns internationally. Her little face also graced countless covers of magazines, posters and toy boxes. Taylor remained in school while enjoying her young career. She graduated from high school in 2014 a year early and with honors and attends the University of Florida. She has visions of attending medical school. Taylor participates actively in dog rescue. She most recently helped rescue a pit-bull who was wandering homeless on the "Bloodline" set from the dog-fighting streets of Homestead, Florida. She also owns seven of her own rescue dogs. An avid football fan, Taylor enjoys sports, both playing them and watching them.
